(44, 19, 11, 43, 14, 12, 12, 'special miracles', 'Miraculous Works of Believers', 'Both passages emphasize the ability to perform miracles. Acts 19:11 describes Paul performing special miracles, while John 14:12 states that believers will do greater works. This connection highlights the continuity of miraculous works through faith.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
