(44, 19, 15, 44, 16, 17, 18, 'Jesus I know, and Paul I know', 'Authority of Jesus and Paul', 'This connection highlights the recognition of Jesus and Paul by the evil spirit in Acts 19:15, paralleling the authority demonstrated by Paul in casting out the spirit in Acts 16:17-18. Both passages emphasize the power of the name of Jesus in spiritual matters.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
